# Registraton OTP Verification: 
* step-1: Submit registration form.
* step-2: Go to controller where submitted data are storing.
          - now default status will be inactive.
          - store status, OTP_Code, otp_expire_at (DateTime - this will setup from settings), 
* step-3: after store above data, show a modal where OTP code will be insert.
          - if modal otp code, mobile_no is matched with database otp_code and mobile_no then user will be active.
